   <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
         <p class="intro_text">
            Use our free software to configure your Speck and optionally register it to upload its data to your
            account on specksensor.com. Alternatively, you can use the Speck software to download the data directly to
            your computer.
         </p>
         <p style="text-align: center; margin:50px">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/speck/anchbeboblnigmihhclbdkpdglecnimi" role="button"><i class="fa fa-download"></i> Download</a>
         </p>
         <p class="fine_print">
            The Speck app is available for free on the Chrome Web Store. The Speck app requires Google Chrome on either
            Windows or Mac OS 10.8+.
         </p>
